| 1AFB26CC1DA5441115D00D57EC627EF5 |         2 |    2 | select * from t2 where c1 > 100/0 |
+----------------------------------+-----------+------+-----------------------------------+

pre calculate error when rewrite or calc selectivity, do not add constraint
select * from t2 where c2 > 100/0;
select * from t2 where c2 > 100/1;
