| B7B8FC10C24D787184CBB420847E9F60 |         4 |    1 | select * from t4 where c2 like concat(?,?)     |
| B7B8FC10C24D787184CBB420847E9F60 |         4 |    2 | select * from t4 where c2 like concat('a','%') |
+----------------------------------+-----------+------+------------------------------------------------+

like pattern used to calc table location, do not add constraint
